<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.183825>
    dc:description "FIGURE 10.? Bairdoppilata sp. 1 aff.? B. labiata. Legend: A – K, A M (USNM 121348); L – O, A F (USNM 121347). A, C, LV hinge; B, LV, iv; D, F, RV hinge; E, N, RV iv; G, I, normal pore canals; H, posterior of LV, ev; J, adductor muscle scars of LV; K, anterior of LV, ev; L, posterior of RV, ev; M, O, RV lateral surface. Scale bars: A, C, D, F, O, 10 µm; B, E, N, 500 µm; G, I, 1 µm; J, H, L, 100 µm; K, M, 50 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/183825/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

